Definition: helpful in bringing about a harmonious adaptation
Example: the warden was always accommodating in allowing visitors in; made a special effort to be accommodating
Synonyms: UNACCOMMODATING, accommodative, verb, communication, accommodate, GOOD-NATURED, HELPFUL, KIND, helpful, in, bringing, about, a, harmonious, adaptation, the, warden, was, always, accommodating, allowing, visitors, made, special, effort, to, be
Category: adj.all
